= aGrep again

A modern fork of aGrep - Grep-like text search program for Android.

This is a maintained and updated version of the original aGrep application,
originally developed by Jiro and Aquamarine Networks.

Supported OS: Android 7.0 (Nougat) and above (minSdk 24)

== Original aGrep Information

The original aGrep application:
* Android Market: http://market.android.com/details?id=jp.sblo.pandora.aGrep
* Documentation (English): https://sites.google.com/site/aquamarinepandora/home/agrep
* Documentation (Japanese): https://sites.google.com/site/aquamarinepandora/home/agrepja


== Development Environment
* Android Studio
* Android SDK (compileSdk 34, targetSdk 34)
* Repository: https://github.com/kappa/aGrep-again

